== 6...Nf6 ==

'''6...Nf6''' develops while threatening White's e4 pawn. 

White can defend with [[/7. N1c3|'''7. N1c3''']], developing their second knight and intending their other knight to retreat to a3, or '''7. N5c3''', leaving their knight on b1 undeveloped for now. 

